HEADWORD: Chichevache
<hw>Chiche"vache`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>chiche</ets> lean + <ets>vache</ets> cow.]</ety> <def>A fabulous
cow of enormous size, whose food was patient wives, and which was
therefore in very lean condition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

